<br>
Today at work, a friend and coworker was asked to remove from plain sight his band's logo and cell phone case, both of which feature the Confederate Flag, because someone had filed a complaint with Human Resources. The band logo has been on display almost two years prior to today and his phone case is about 6 months old.<br>
<br>
How do you feel about the flag? <br>
<br>
I'm posting here in Rants because the issue can get people riled up. Keep the discussion civil and please share your thoughts. If a choice doesn't apply, please feel free to explain your own view point.<br>
