<br>
Surely you southerners crack jokes about northerners. It doesn't mean you hate them. (Or, maybe you do hate them.) It doesn't mean they are worse than you are. (Or, maybe you really do believe they are worse than you are.) All it means is that they are different in some ways than the people you are used to being around. <br>
<br>
There are differences in every culture. Living in the south will give most people a certain cultural background that is particular to this region of the U.S. That's just the way it is. But, surely, it does not apply to *every* single person that is from a specific region. There are variances in every culture or any sample of people. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=651.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=651.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=651.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=651.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=651.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showMessageRange?topicID=651.topic&start=121&stop=134>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=651.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showNextMessage?topicID=651.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=651.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.jennymarie.com/eqp/03reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=651.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub141.ezboard.com/feverquestpeoplefrm7.threadControl?topicID=6